Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.35,0:00:10.36,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong!{lines 1-8 have been replaced with our last episode dialogue-Kevo}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.36,0:00:12.10,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,That ain't even close!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.10,0:00:13.11,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.11,0:00:14.58,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I played it exactly right!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.58,0:00:16.11,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,There wasn't any {\i1}swing{\i0}{\fs30} {\fs54}!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.11,0:00:19.08,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,If you play it without feelin', it ain't jazz to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.08,0:00:23.50,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ricchan, do you know the name of the tune he was playing on the piano?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.75,0:00:27.46,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Art Blakey and the Jazz Messengers' "Moanin'."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.22,0:02:16.44,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My aunt's gone grocery shopping for dinner.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.93,0:02:18.64,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've got one hour to make it or break it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.93,0:02:26.20,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dissonant chords... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.20,0:02:28.87,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Syncopation and a unique accent...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.33,0:02:39.63,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I thought I understood the distinctive features of jazz in my head,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.63,0:02:42.24,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but reproducing them is proving to be extremely difficult.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.09,0:03:10.37,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This guy doesn't get jazz at all!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.37,0:03:12.00,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And he's got no sense for it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.16,0:03:13.29,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.29,0:03:15.92,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what it takes, I'm gonna show him up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.99,0:03:45.48,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to master this as soon as possible{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.48,0:03:47.99,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and then perform it in front of him and Ricchan!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.63,0:03:52.35,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You win...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.35,0:03:55.00,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san, that was wonderful...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.21,0:03:56.68,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As if...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.68,0:03:58.31,Default,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well. Nishimi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.39,0:04:01.43,Default,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,You sure look like you're in a good mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.87,0:04:03.01,Default,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,Where ya goin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.96,0:04:07.41,Default,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make a fuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.60,0:04:10.49,Default,Tokieda,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.64,0:04:15.81,Default,Tokieda,0000,0000,0000,,Ricchan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.81,0:04:16.85,Default,Tokieda,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.10,0:04:21.24,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.49,0:04:22.94,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What did I ever do to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.28,0:04:25.11,Default,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,It's my neck, is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.88,0:04:30.80,Default,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,These days, I've got a crick in my neck that just won't quit,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.24,0:04:32.85,Default,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,an' it's puttin' me in the worst mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.15,0:04:36.24,Default,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,So I thought havin' a little fun like this would brighten my day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.81,0:04:37.99,Default,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,Other than that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.34,0:04:40.63,Default,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,...you've kind of been gettin' on my nerves lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.58,0:04:44.19,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.35,0:04:50.10,Default,Boy B,0000,0000,0000,,He's in the kendo club, so you'd better not resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.75,0:04:55.16,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.09,0:04:58.22,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,There's trouble! Come quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.00,0:05:00.36,Default,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.36,0:05:01.98,Default,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,How can we entertain ourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.98,0:05:03.22,Default,Boy A,0000,0000,0000,,How about splitting a watermelon?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.05,0:05:05.28,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.68,0:05:08.02,Default,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,We can do better than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.02,0:05:09.94,Default,Boy C,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say we pants 'im?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.28,0:05:11.43,Default,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,Now there's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.03,0:05:13.71,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.97,0:05:15.12,Default,Boy A,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.12,0:05:16.66,Default,Boy A,0000,0000,0000,,Keep nice an' quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.15,0:05:19.91,Default,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,Students from the girls' school come home this way too,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.91,0:05:22.12,Default,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,so this'll give them a good show.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.18,0:05:35.99,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Too much momentum...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.04,0:05:38.99,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.50,0:05:42.02,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, when this jerk wakes up,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.55,0:05:45.23,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,tell 'im that no real man gangs up on a weakling...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.25,0:05:47.19,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, it's you, Bon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.19,0:05:49.20,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, sorry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.61,0:05:52.73,Default,Boy A,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you okay, Yamaoka-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.34,0:05:54.95,Default,Boy C,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Your front tooth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.95,0:05:57.82,Default,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you guys just standing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.82,0:05:59.30,Default,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care how you do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.30,0:06:01.33,Default,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,I just want you to kill that guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.46,0:06:04.84,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.24,0:06:08.67,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna play a game like "monkey in the middle"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.45,0:06:11.96,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no... At this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.64,0:06:17.07,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,R-Ricchan! What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.07,0:06:19.48,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro will take care of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.48,0:06:20.65,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,so get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.60,0:06:27.19,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Clearly, you boys ain't used to scrappin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.88,0:06:31.07,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I look pathetic.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.55,0:06:34.90,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ricchan literally caught me with my pants down.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.90,0:06:37.47,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And on top of that, she rescued me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.53,0:06:43.98,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ricchan, would you hold on to my glasses for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.46,0:06:50.57,Default,Boy A,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.53,0:07:02.35,Default,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll pay you back for knocking out my front tooth!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.47,0:07:12.13,Default,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.40,0:07:15.22,Default,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,Is he dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.05,0:07:19.70,Default,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,You little twerp!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.41,0:07:22.44,Default,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,Get 'im!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.08,0:07:27.47,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.75,0:07:29.67,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's startin' to get interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.83,0:07:37.69,Default,Boy A,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.93,0:07:47.77,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Well? You up for some more?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.83,0:07:53.66,Default,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm gonna see to it that everyone in class gives you the cold shoulder!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.66,0:07:54.59,Default,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.22,0:07:56.86,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,You an' me are in the same class?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.46,0:07:59.61,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Can't remember seein' this guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.61,0:08:01.62,Default,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,B-Be prepared!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.35,0:08:04.51,Default,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? My neck feels better.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.12,0:08:08.05,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san, your forehead is bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.05,0:08:09.09,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.09,0:08:10.87,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry 'bout his forehead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.39,0:08:14.13,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Are your... fingers okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.28,0:08:20.89,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh? He's actually looking out for me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.46,0:08:24.52,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.82,0:08:27.46,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you took another pounding, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.24,0:08:29.52,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody's waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.99,0:08:30.98,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Go on downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.57,0:08:33.16,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be Jun-nii?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.01,0:08:36.16,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.05,0:08:40.63,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Why is the squirt beat up too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.63,0:08:42.19,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,He was in a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.10,0:08:44.42,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Jun-nii!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.42,0:08:45.23,Default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.46,0:08:49.46,Default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Sen-bou, you've been gettin' rowdy again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:52.60,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, well, today wasn't much of a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.79,0:08:55.16,Default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's good to see you're in fighting form.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.16,0:08:57.34,Default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,So, who's this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.43,0:08:59.76,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,He's my buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.76,0:09:01.97,Default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Huh. Cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.97,0:09:03.38,Default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,An odd couple, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.38,0:09:03.99,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.76,0:09:07.24,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, we're not friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.69,0:09:13.99,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ah, well...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.03,0:09:19.90,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Say, is he your brother, Ricchan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.21,0:09:24.04,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,No, Jun-nii-chan is our neighbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:26.70,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to a university in Tokyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.70,0:09:27.53,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Ritsuko...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.91,0:09:30.52,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Mind the store for just one tune.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.52,0:09:33.34,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, you always say "just one tune",
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.34,0:09:35.27,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,but then you don't come up for two hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.27,0:09:38.14,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,It's not every day that Junichi comes back to town, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.40,0:09:41.34,Default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Ricchan, I'm asking you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.34,0:09:45.05,Default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, I'll treat you to a cream soda at our shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.17,0:09:47.81,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Throw in a choux à la crème?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.81,0:09:49.02,Default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.48,0:09:52.88,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! We've got us a deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.88,0:09:53.56,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get started!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.95,0:09:56.58,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wh-What?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.47,0:10:10.14,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A live session...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.10,0:10:23.51,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Bon, get over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.51,0:10:24.57,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.66,0:10:26.80,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.80,0:10:29.47,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Just make some noise, that's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.27,0:10:44.24,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What are you so jittery for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.64,0:10:46.86,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Don't sweat the details. Just jump in!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.85,0:11:45.20,Default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? So you've only been playing jazz for two weeks?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.20,0:11:46.72,Default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.72,0:11:48.77,Default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,It was all over the place,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:50.36,Default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,but you got the mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.64,0:11:52.19,Default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,You've played piano for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.19,0:11:53.97,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.82,0:11:57.98,Default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,How about coming over here from now on to practice?{shorten if possible}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.99,0:12:01.26,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,He'll come every day even without being told, right?{ditto}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.50,0:12:06.44,Default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I have to get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.88,0:12:08.30,Default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Ricchan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.43,0:12:10.60,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right, Jun-nii.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.40,0:12:13.67,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What's the name of that record you were tellin' me about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.67,0:12:16.00,Default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the Elvin Jones one?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.00,0:12:18.18,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's it. "Tommy" something...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.18,0:12:19.63,Default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,"Flanagan."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.63,0:12:20.99,Default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.51,0:12:22.93,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The two of us are alone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.13,0:12:27.38,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Um, say...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.00,0:12:32.39,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ricchan, what do you usually do on your days off?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.39,0:12:34.77,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you mean with summer vacation coming up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.77,0:12:36.52,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.52,0:12:38.19,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking maybe
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.19,0:12:40.89,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,we could do our homework together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.89,0:12:42.36,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.36,0:12:44.69,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I bet I could make real progress working on it with you, Kaoru-san.{holmie is making his move (:}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.36,0:12:47.07,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,How's next Sunday?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.44,0:12:49.18,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Would 11 work?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.18,0:12:50.66,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.66,0:12:53.92,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I know! Let's meet up behind the church.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.86,0:12:58.31,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on. I'll draw you a map.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.94,0:13:02.09,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.53,0:13:03.92,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Summer vacation...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.02,0:13:08.03,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Up until now, I've spent my summer vacations alone in my room{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.03,0:13:10.93,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}with far too much time on my hands.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.77,0:13:13.10,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What should I do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.10,0:13:15.37,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have so many things to look forward to{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.37,0:13:17.27,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that I can't wrap my head around it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.22,0:13:22.94,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I'm a little early.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.86,0:13:38.44,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, church on Sunday morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.94,0:13:52.05,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ricchan...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.70,0:13:55.77,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...is a Christian?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.10,0:14:05.31,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.38,0:14:08.74,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Him too?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.37,0:14:18.71,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.07,0:14:20.65,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to make you wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.65,0:14:22.23,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay. Well, should we...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.23,0:14:23.16,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.62,0:14:25.42,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.42,0:14:26.30,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.19,0:14:34.30,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is how we're going to the library?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.07,0:14:40.73,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or rather, why is he with us?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.69,0:14:48.69,Default,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2\bord0\shad0\pos(645,207)\fscx51.25\fscy61.25\c&H0E0E0E&}Kashimae Pier
