Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.91,0:14:50.54,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Um... What about the library?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.54,0:14:52.03,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,It's so hot today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.03,0:14:53.73,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't it feel much better at the ocean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.94,0:14:56.20,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro agreed this was the way to go too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.97,0:15:01.47,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ricchan... I meant for this to be a date.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.06,0:15:03.21,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.21,0:15:05.20,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I rented a boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.94,0:15:07.21,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hop in!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.46,0:15:14.50,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How did it come to this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.84,0:15:16.64,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why'd it end up being the three of us?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.51,0:15:22.14,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Bon, give me a bite of that, would ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.17,0:15:25.10,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the face?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.10,0:15:26.85,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't the rower get any kind of reward for his services?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.85,0:15:29.28,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro, you can finish this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.28,0:15:31.15,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,No, he can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.15,0:15:32.31,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.31,0:15:35.41,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, uh... Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.41,0:15:36.85,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Here, eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.63,0:15:42.35,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,One bite, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.14,0:15:54.16,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ricchan, do you always have a cross on too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.16,0:15:57.07,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Nope. I have a rosary,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.07,0:15:59.79,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,but it's not something you're supposed to wear around your neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.12,0:16:03.21,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Our priest says Sentaro is special, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.21,0:16:04.01,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Rikko...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.67,0:16:06.54,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to tell him all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.07,0:16:12.51,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For just a second there, the tension was thick enough to cut with a knife.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.06,0:16:14.32,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or was it just my imagination?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.78,0:16:18.16,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Wahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.96,0:16:22.87,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san, aren't you going to swim?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.99,0:16:27.37,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,We came all this way, so let's take a dip!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.08,0:16:32.38,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,The thing is, I didn't bring along a bathing suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.67,0:16:36.83,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Neither did Sentaro. He's just wearing his undies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.53,0:16:40.05,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Let's swim, Kaoru-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.17,0:16:43.05,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.05,0:16:46.43,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Rikko, hurry up and dive in!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.43,0:16:48.23,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.09,0:16:50.90,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What are you bein' bashful about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.90,0:16:52.44,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,You're flat as a washboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.82,0:16:56.99,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Last time we went swimmin', you had nothin' but your slip on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.99,0:17:00.59,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, for goodness' sake! That was when we were in elementary school!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.15,0:17:04.43,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say weird things like that in front of Kaoru-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.86,0:17:06.38,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Enough, Sentaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.87,0:17:05.83,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ricchan...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.62,0:17:08.42,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Could it be you...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.04,0:17:10.83,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Rikko, pinch your nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.58,0:17:13.21,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.62,0:17:16.36,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Alley-oop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.58,0:17:19.55,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ricchan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.55,0:17:20.70,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ricchan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.70,0:17:21.92,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Bon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.24,0:17:28.81,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Geez! You're such a meanie, Sentaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.21,0:17:33.06,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,It feels good, doesn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.06,0:17:35.95,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,He really is a jerk, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.10,0:17:40.66,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Kaoru-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.66,0:17:42.57,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you keep swimming in circles?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.37,0:17:47.96,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,This is the only way I know how to swim with my head out of the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.13,0:17:50.95,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san, you're a funny guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.36,0:17:53.71,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She laughed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.59,0:17:58.51,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why do I feel so happy when she smiles?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.47,0:18:07.14,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh... I feel like I could do anything for that smile.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.48,0:18:13.65,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you two look like you're havin' fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.65,0:18:14.73,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Let me join in!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.09,0:18:16.40,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.40,0:18:18.38,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ricchan, let's get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.94,0:18:20.36,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san, wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.63,0:18:22.74,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what gives?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.74,0:18:24.50,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you swimmin' away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.67,0:18:32.92,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, I only wish that we could keep going...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.92,0:18:35.83,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That I could take you away from here...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.63,0:19:01.56,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Let's trade places.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.26,0:19:05.03,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take over the rowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.03,0:19:07.45,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty hard, y'know. And on top of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.45,0:19:08.46,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Just let me do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.64,0:19:13.78,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.10,0:19:15.73,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna switch, Bon?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.73,0:19:18.84,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not about strength. It's about technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.13,0:19:21.46,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,And I think I'm getting the hang of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.93,0:19:23.72,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I'm complainin'...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.12,0:19:26.47,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,...but you've been takin' us in circles.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.89,0:19:30.98,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.98,0:19:34.09,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,You took us to a completely different beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.98,0:19:36.98,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.30,0:19:39.03,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,The sun is already setting anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.03,0:19:40.70,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,so if we tell the boat rental guy what happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.70,0:19:41.99,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,he'll come by and pick it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.49,0:19:49.61,Default,Man 2,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, miss, have a little fun with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.96,0:19:52.73,Default,Man 2,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so stuck-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.73,0:19:54.62,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,No! Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.62,0:19:56.38,Default,Man 1,0000,0000,0000,,We ain't gonna hurt ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.38,0:19:57.57,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.11,0:20:00.81,Default,Man 1,0000,0000,0000,,We got a car, so let us take you for a ride!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.81,0:20:02.23,Default,Man 1,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.51,0:20:05.21,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. The lady ain't willin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.61,0:20:07.05,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,So how about gettin' your mitts off her?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.37,0:20:09.62,Default,Man 1,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?! Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.62,0:20:11.77,Default,Man 1,0000,0000,0000,,Actin' so tough...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.77,0:20:14.14,Default,Man 1,0000,0000,0000,,What, are you tryin' to be a hero?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.14,0:20:18.04,Default,Man 3,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that guy is East High's Kawabuchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.37,0:20:21.11,Default,Man 1,0000,0000,0000,,East High... You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.06,0:20:23.19,Default,Man 1,0000,0000,0000,,Kawabuchi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.19,0:20:33.20,Default,Man 1,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This time, I'll let you off the hook.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.79,0:20:39.00,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,You saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.19,0:20:54.44,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.87,0:21:01.28,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It happened in an instant.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.73,0:21:06.95,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I didn't realize what had just taken place.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.37,0:21:13.77,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But when it comes to falling in love, you don't need a reason or time.{\i0}
